Package edu.nd.darts.cimon

Interface Summary
AdminObservable Interface for custom observer framework used to provide updates to CIMON administration app.
AdminUpdate Defines interface used for updating values in the administration app.
CimonInterface API provided for CIMON service.
CurrentNode<T> Interface which defines nodes that maintain triple-linked-list structure for all actively monitored metrics.
ExpressionNode Node within a ConditionTree.
KeyGenerator Deprecated.  
ObservableUpdate Interface for method to update observables after addition of observer.
